p
  | By using the Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.
  | Personal information is used solely to provide and improve the Service and is not shared except as described here.

p
  strong Information Collection and Use

p
  | For a better experience, I may ask you to provide certain personally identifiable information, such as your name
  | and workout data. Workout data is stored on your device and, if you choose to enable syncing or sharing, on
  | servers solely to facilitate those features.

p
  | Workout data is encrypted end to end on the client. Encryption keys are generated and held only on your device.
  | LiftLog servers cannot read or access your workout content.

p
  | Only you and the people you explicitly choose to share workouts with can decrypt and view your workout data.

